bcunit
------------------------------------------
This is BCUnit, a fork of the defunct project CUnit, with several fixes and
patches applied.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.2.0-1
  libbcunit-devel-3.0.2+git20210211-1bl1
  libbcunit0-3.0.2+git20210211-1bl1
  libncurses-devel-6.1-1.20190727
  libncursesw10-6.1-1.20190727
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-1
  cmake-3.20.0-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.2.0-1
  libncurses-devel-6.1-1.20190727
  ninja-1.10.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bcunit-3.0.2+git20210211-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bcunit-3.0.2+git20210211-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bcunit-3.0.2+git20210211-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bcunit-3.0.2+git20210211-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit0-3.0.2+git20210211-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit-devel-3.0.2+git20210211-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

